			<h1 id="hctra-ez-tag-application-agreement">HCTRA EZ TAG Account Numbers Reference</h1>

			<p>Each tag&rsquo;s identification number starts with 4 letters (&ldquo;HCTR&rdquo;, if you purchased your tag from HCTRA) and ends with 8 digits.</p>

			<p><em>Example:</em> HCTR 12345678</p>

